Endpoint	Method	Description	
`/health`	GET	Server status	
`/api/mpesa/stk-push`	POST	Initiate M-Pesa payment	
`/api/mpesa/callback`	POST	M-Pesa webhook	
`/api/orders`	GET/POST	Order management	
`/api/orders/:id/status`	PUT	Update order status	
`/api/web3/verify-eth`	POST	Verify ETH transaction	
`/api/web3/verify-sol`	POST	Verify SOL transaction	
`/ws`	WebSocket	Real-time updates
